// Shared Windows resource script: gives every Cat Splat executable the studio
// icon (Explorer, taskbar, alt-tab). The resource is named GLFW_ICON because
// that is the name GLFW's Win32 backend looks up for the window-class icon —
// one resource covers both the file icon and the live window.
//
// To change the icon, regenerate resources/CatSplat.ico with
// scripts/make_icon.py (see its header for the exact command) — no code or
// build changes needed.
GLFW_ICON ICON "CatSplat.ico"
